article.headline: McHenry scores 16, Western Kentucky downs Buffalo 82-65
article.description: — Don McHenry scored 16 points as Western Kentucky beat Buffalo 82-65 on Saturday.
article.linkText: McHenry scores 16, Western Kentucky downs Buffalo 82-65
article.story: BUFFALO, N.Y. -- — Don McHenry scored 16 points as Western Kentucky beat Buffalo 82-65 on Saturday. McHenry shot 5 of 7 from the field and 5 for 5 from the line for the Hilltoppers (7-3). Brandon Newman scored 11 points and added eight rebounds. The Bulls (1-9) were led in scoring by Sy Chatman, who finished with 21 points, 11 rebounds, two steals and three blocks. Anquan Boldin Jr. added 19 points and two steals for Buffalo. Ryan Sabol also put up 12 points and seven assists. The loss is the seventh in a row for the Bulls. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
